Deathrun_Goldfever_a
====================
Map by FireWavezZ
-----------------

This is a detailed western themed death run map with TF2 props.
Worked a very long time on it, and it's being tested many many times before we got this final result.

Map specs:

- 2 T spawns with extra speed

- 37 CT spawns

- 23 traps

- 3 secret smoke grenades

- 4 minigames + 1 bonus
